Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了…我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（想死）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（妈妈）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在犹豫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想通点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（杀）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（妈妈）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（把孩子还给我）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（救救我）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（不理解）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（这个痛苦）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（你也到这边来）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}再会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（All right All right）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（好 就这样）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在那边的废工厂看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一个很大的铠甲带着走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铠甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅 那个铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然掳走小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜裆男
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个胖家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得是叫人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以认为是拥有不死的再生能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法轻易出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死身？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了 那不是能轻易对付的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那两人会在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这个国家以后一直感到不协调
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚下有很多不知道什么东西爬来爬去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？很冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央都市的地下居然有这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这些是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是门卫干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门卫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起就不会被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很长的路？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还很长哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道被吞下的人在哪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人什么都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩维的核
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我出来 恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助我 恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面果然有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合成兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人制造了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 拉斯多 还有恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不记得双亲的名字和面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至连自己的名字也不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是在取名之前被丢弃了或者被卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背负这个国家的会是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统候补
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被这么称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被集中到一处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受各种各样的教育
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帝王学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有军队格斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑术等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是达成你目的的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己会成为推动这个国家的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如此坚信着忍耐了各种各样的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些尸体是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十二个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受我的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石是包含了大量人类意识的高能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦放入人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会发生排斥反应 会想占据人的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石头导致的破坏和修补
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使原来的身体死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者直到战胜贤者之石为止一直重复下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:11:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被我们选作为领导这个国家的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人会准备好你所需要的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字从今天开始就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就只有一个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和愤怒这一感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个灵魂是被做成贤者之石的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是原来的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经无从知晓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果原来是人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不能不作人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而作为人类活下去吗 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变回人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体超越了人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远优越于人类的品质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你们作为人类有着人类的自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有作为人造人的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人也是抱着这份自尊而死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急处理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这附近的全部收齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些…全都是克塞鲁克塞斯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遗迹神殿里大壁画的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到那个壁画的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为和第五研究所地下的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是贤者之石的炼成阵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳是灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮表示精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后作为壁画载体的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这表示肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 简单说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画在那里的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体炼成的阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体炼成？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 能让死者苏醒的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 炼金术的原则是等价交换
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让不存在于这个世界的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用炼成来产生是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点已经被证实了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我想到了离开这里的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把自己重新炼成会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新炼成？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用这个炼成阵把自己分解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再构筑成自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门一定会打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说库拉多尼是虚假的真理之门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么穿过正确的门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就能到达正确的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跳进里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失败了会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,术的失败会全部反弹到施术者身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的情况会反弹到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对于炼金术是门外汉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩维 有件事要问你？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见到的克塞鲁克塞斯大壁画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上是这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在意的是这个记号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示神的文字上下颠倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 双头的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个表示完美的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把神打落地面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己成为完美的存在之意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真是在考虑不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是考虑也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缺少的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞下太阳的狮子图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这表示贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石的材料是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么繁荣的克塞鲁克塞斯国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一夜之间就毁灭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国民到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有遗迹的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是为了消灭证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把克塞鲁克塞斯全部国民…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.03,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了贤者之石吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成自己的是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把全部国民变成贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到那强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成为超越神的存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你所说的父亲大人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他使用你们人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是想在这个国家重现克塞鲁克塞斯的灭亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能从这里出去的话 就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拐弯抹角的话题就到这里为止吧 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要打开门的话 需要的是通行费吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（救救我）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60}（杀了我）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是克塞鲁克塞斯的人民吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉体和精神早就不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是作为被消费的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己原来是什么样子也不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是同情吗 真是无聊的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想要承认只有灵魂存在的弟弟是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想要承认这些相似的东西是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会觉得远古时代灭亡的树太可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而犹豫是否要给石炭加上火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙已经无法再变回人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是靠感情而是根据道理来定义人类
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟 如果我出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把这些家伙的企图告诉外面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美斯多利斯变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是等着你回去的人所住的国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己去告诉他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我使用你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那合掌的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得像什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是向神的祈祷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会以这种形式再次打开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟 跳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和被库拉多尼吞下去的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉体和灵魂由精神联系着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的肉体的一部分就在真理之门的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着精神的引导
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一切托付
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着门…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是来夺回身体的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人就在里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有哥哥的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会有两扇门？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.05,0:21:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一起过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:24:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影和火焰的跳动相似
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难捕捉到它的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后火焰有时非常残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第27话 夹缝的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能恐惧自己心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:12.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:30.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:43.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:27.01,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:33.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:37.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:44.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.12,0:22:49.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:55.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:57.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:23:01.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:08.91,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:16.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:22.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:27.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:32.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:38.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:44.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:48.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:52.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:56.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
